{"type":"message","id":"0661e597","parentId":"d262a846","timestamp":"2026-03-03T11:04:18.430Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_qjbteio72pps_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"query\":\"real time stock price API\",\"total\":3,\"results\":[{\"tool_id\":\"financialmodelingprep.historical_chart.15min.retrieve.v1.f95a7510\",\"name\":\"Retrieve 15-Minute Interval Historical Chart Data\",\"description\":\"Access stock price and volume data with the FMP 15-Minute Interval Stock Chart API. Retrieve detailed stock data in 15-minute intervals, including open, high, low, close prices, and trading volume. This API is ideal for creating intraday charts and analyzing medium-term price trends during the trading day.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"symbol\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Stock symbol\"}}],\"examples\":{\"sample_parameters\":{\"symbol\":\"AAPL\"}},\"provider_description\":\"FMP offers a stock market data API covers real-time stock prices, historical prices and market news to stock fundamentals and company information. We provide one of the most accurate financial data available on the market. You can get historical prices, fundamental data, insider transactions, and much more that goes back 30 years in history.\",\"stats\":{\"avg_execution_time_ms\":1.724,\"success_rate\":1.0}},{\"tool_id\":\"financialmodelingprep.historical_chart.30min.retrieve.v1.65bcce0a\",\"name\":\"Retrieve 30-Minute Interval Historical Chart Data\",\"description\":\"Access stock price and volume data with the FMP 30-Minute Interval Stock Chart API. Retrieve essential stock data in 30-minute intervals, including open, high, low, close prices, and trading volume. This API is perfect for creating intraday charts and tracking medium-term price movements for more strategic trading decisions.\",\"params\":[{\"name\":\"symbol\",\"type\":\"string\",\"required\":true,\"description\":{\"en\":\"Stock symbol\"}}],\"examples\":{\"s