{"type":"message","id":"cf6a5b04","parentId":"f00462d9","timestamp":"2026-03-03T11:06:59.482Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The Finnhub tool still has the parameter issue. This appears to be a bug specific to the Finnhub integration in QVeris. \n\nSince:\n1. Finnhub tools in QVeris are broken (return \"missing required parameter\" error)\n2. EODHD news works and provides sentiment scores\n\nI should inform the user about this limitation and provide the EODHD news as an alternative. The EODHD data includes sentiment polarity which can serve as the \"heat\" score.\n\nLet me now analyze the news data to find items with sentiment ≥ 0.80 (which equals heat score ≥ 80 on a 0-100 scale).","thinkingSignature":"45fdab98f1d97b737273d60db582420178390ee5ad25c0f2dab8e0cee8a92677"},{"type":"text","text":"Finnhub工具在QVeris中存在参数传递问题，无法正常获取数据。EODHD新闻API可以正常使用并提供情感评分。我将使用EODHD的财经新闻作为替代，并筛选热度≥80的新闻推送给您。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_blazdm6qxisw_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s -X POST \"https://qveris.ai/api/v1/tools/execute\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $QVERIS_API_KEY\" \\\n  -d '{\"tool_id\": \"eodhd.news.retrieve.v1.fe8bf94c\", \"params\": {\"t\": \"general\", \"limit\": 50}}' | jq -r '.result.truncated_content' | jq -r '.[] | select(.sentiment.polarity >= 0.80) | \"标题: \\(.title)\\n热度: \\(.sentiment.polarity * 100 | floor)\\n链接: \\(.link)\\n相关股票: \\(.symbols | join(\", \"))\\n\\n\"' 2>/dev/null | head -40","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":41459,"output":384,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55827,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772536010432}}
